# make_argocd_fly
A project to generate ArgoCD application resources

# Install
```
python -m venv .venv
. .venv/bin/activate
python3 -m pip install --upgrade pip
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

# Run
```
python make_argocd_fly/main.py --root-dir <path>
```
